Individual




Gary G. Allison



Mr. Gary G. Allison, Jr., is Vice President-Engineering at Bazaarvoice, Inc. Mr. Allison was previously employed as Vice President-Engineering by Convio, Inc., Senior Vice President-Software Development by Simdesk Technologies, Inc., and Vice President-Engineering & Customer Services by Pervasive Software, Inc. He received his undergraduate degree from Texas A&M University and a graduate degree from the University of Houston-Clear Lake.



